      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical flows must demonstrate expected convergence rates.",
      "rationale": "Method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) tests confirm second-order spatial convergence for the pressure-velocity coupling scheme on structured and unstructured meshes. Results archived in the code verification report CVR-2023-07."
