      "rationale": "Validation data span Q = 3–7 L/min and N = 2000–3000 rpm, fully bracketing the five COU operating points. Geometric similarity maintained using the same FDA generic pump geometry. Fluid analogue properties match blood viscosity at 37 °C within 3%."
