      "acceptanceCriteria": "Physical test samples must be representative of the device geometry used in the simulation.",
      "rationale": "Three pump specimens manufactured to nominal drawing dimensions used for in-vitro testing. CMM inspection confirmed all critical dimensions within ±0.03 mm of nominal. Same nominal geometry used in CFD model; manufacturing variability treated as a sensitivity parameter in the model inputs assessment."
