      "rationale": "This factor was judged by the assessment team to not apply to the current COU because the validation experiments were conducted on the identical pump geometry and fluid analogue used in the clinical application, making a formal equivalency mapping unnecessary. No structured equivalency analysis was performed and no evidence package was assembled. The factor is therefore carried as not-assessed rather than formally scoped out or demonstrated as not-applicable."
