    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed and all meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was judged by the assessment team to be inapplicable given the direct correspondence between validation and COU geometry and fluid conditions; it is carried as not-assessed. The overall credibility evidence is considered sufficient to support the decision that the CFD model adequately predicts worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
